methods.name: GetCustomBoneInfluenceLimit
methods.doc:
Query the maximum number of bone influences to allow each vertex in this mesh to use.
If set higher than the limit determined by the project settings, it has no effect.
If set to 0, the value is taken from the DefaultBoneInfluenceLimit project setting.

methods.name: GetCustomCreatePhysicsAsset
methods.doc: Query whether the skeletal mesh factory should create a physics asset. Return false if the attribute was not set.

methods.name: GetCustomImportContentType
methods.doc: Query the skeletal mesh import content type. This content type determines whether the factory imports partial or full translated content. Return false if the attribute was not set.

methods.name: GetCustomImportMorphTarget
methods.doc: Query whether the skeletal mesh factory should create morph targets. Return false if the attribute was not set.

methods.name: GetCustomImportVertexAttributes
methods.doc: Query whether the skeletal mesh factory should import vertex attributes. Return false if the attribute was not set.

methods.name: GetCustomMorphThresholdPosition
methods.doc: Query the skeletal mesh threshold value that is used to compare vertex position equality when computing morph target deltas.

methods.name: GetCustomPhysicAssetSoftObjectPath
methods.doc: Query a physics asset the skeletal mesh factory should use. Return false if the attribute was not set.

methods.name: GetCustomSkeletonSoftObjectPath
methods.doc: Query the skeletal mesh factory skeleton UObject. Return false if the attribute was not set.

methods.name: GetCustomThresholdPosition
methods.doc: Query the skeletal mesh threshold value that is used to decide whether two vertex positions are equal.

methods.name: GetCustomThresholdTangentNormal
methods.doc: Query the skeletal mesh threshold value that is used to decide whether two normals, tangents, or bi-normals are equal.

methods.name: GetCustomThresholdUV
methods.doc: Query the skeletal mesh threshold value that is used to decide whether two UVs are equal.

methods.name: GetCustomUseHighPrecisionSkinWeights
methods.doc: Query the skeletal mesh UseHighPrecisionSkinWeights setting.

methods.name: GetObjectClass
methods.doc: Get the class this node creates.
